ent-ActionInfect = Infect
    .desc = Attempt to infect a target. Uses charges.
ent-ActionDiseaseShop = Disease Shop
    .desc = Open the disease mutation menu.
ent-ActionDiseaseBaseChance = Base Chance Upgrade
    .desc = Increases the base infection chance by 10%.
ent-ActionDiseaseInfectChance = Infect Chance Upgrade
    .desc = Increases the cough/sneeze infection chance by 5%.
ent-ActionDiseaseShield = Shield Upgrade
    .desc = Increases disease resistance.
ent-ActionDiseaseLethal = Lethal Upgrade
    .desc = Makes the disease more deadly.
ent-ActionDiseaseInfectCharge = Infect Charge
    .desc = Add 1 charge to your Infect ability.
ent-ActionDiseaseCough = Cough
    .desc = Infected start coughing.
ent-ActionDiseaseSneeze = Sneeze
    .desc = Infected start sneezing.
ent-ActionDiseaseVomit = Nausea
    .desc = Infected feel nauseous, causing vomiting.
ent-ActionDiseaseNarcolepsy = Drowsiness
    .desc = Infected develop a constant desire to sleep, which they sometimes cannot overcome.
ent-ActionDiseaseCrying = Involuntary Tears
    .desc = Infected eyes water actively, making it seem like they are crying.
ent-ActionDiseaseMuted = Muteness
    .desc = Mutation causes damage to the hypoglossal nerve, leading to paralysis of the tongue muscles, causing patients to lose the ability to speak normally.
ent-ActionDiseaseSlowness = Exhaustion
    .desc = The virus causes destruction of muscle fibers, leading to atrophy and accompanied by weakness. Reduces overall mobility.
ent-ActionDiseaseBleed = Blood Loss
    .desc = The virus causes denaturation of blood hemoglobin, causing all carriers to develop severe anemia.
ent-ActionDiseaseBlindness = Blindness
    .desc = Prolonged illness leads to death of the optic nerve, leading to almost complete blindness of the patient.
ent-ActionDiseaseInsult = Convulsions
    .desc = Prolonged illness causes hyperstimulation of motor neurons, as a result of which patients may experience muscle overstrain, leading to convulsions.
ent-ActionDiseaseZombie = Zombification
    .desc = All current infected become zombies. They also stop being infected.
ent-ActionDiseaseInfo = Disease Information
    .desc = View your current disease statistics and progress.


